      <title>南非警方从废弃金矿中打捞出 78 具尸体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-police-retrieve-78-bodies-from-abandoned-gold-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非救援人员从一座废弃的金矿中找到了 78 具尸体，数百名非法采金者在该矿与当局进行了长达数月的对峙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-police-retrieve-78-bodies-from-abandoned-gold-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:18:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国考虑购买更多美国能源以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-considers-buying-more-us-energy-to-appease-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正考虑从美国购买更多石油和天然气，以实现其能源来源多元化，并可能抵御当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-considers-buying-more-us-energy-to-appease-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登贸易主管警告特朗普不要依赖关税来获取收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-warned-against-relying-on-tariffs-for-cash-by-biden-trade-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登即将离任的贸易主管称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普利用关税收入取代所得税的想法“非常非常危险”，并表示此举将损害低收入工人的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-warned-against-relying-on-tariffs-for-cash-by-biden-trade-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特财政部任命听证会值得关注的事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/what-to-watch-for-at-bessent-s-treasury-confirmation-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长的任命听证会通常会为提名人上任后的优先事项和原则定下关键标志，周四的参议院财政委员会听证会成为焦点，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将挑选斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 出任财政部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/what-to-watch-for-at-bessent-s-treasury-confirmation-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国尹某请求法院审查其被捕的合法性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-s-yoon-asks-court-to-review-legitimacy-of-his-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈已请求首尔一家法院复审对他的拘留，因为他周四因未能宣布戒严而再次面临调查人员的讯问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-s-yoon-asks-court-to-review-legitimacy-of-his-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 03:06:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杨忠礼及金务大在安瓦尔访问期间公布 52 亿英镑英国项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ytl-gamuda-unveil-5-2-billion-uk-projects-during-anwar-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣开始访问英国，马来西亚企业集团杨忠礼集团和金务大有限公司宣布在英国投资总计 52 亿英镑（64 亿美元）的房地产项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ytl-gamuda-unveil-5-2-billion-uk-projects-during-anwar-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 02:40:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称中国黑客入侵财政部 400 多台电脑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/treasury-hackers-focused-on-sanctions-intelligence-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻社看到的一份机构报告显示，受中国政府支持的黑客入侵了美国财政部，入侵了 400 多台笔记本电脑和台式电脑，尤其对负责制裁、国际事务和情报工作的工作人员和高级领导人的机器感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/treasury-hackers-focused-on-sanctions-intelligence-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港考虑第二年提高高收入者税负</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港政府正在研究连续第二年对香港高收入者提高税收，以弥补预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大被竞争对手指控倾销乳制品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰、澳大利亚和美国乳制品公司指责加拿大向国际市场倾销低价乳制品，并要求其政府进行干预。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/canada-accused-by-rival-dairy-exporters-of-dumping-milk-products</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 21:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默对乌克兰的谨慎态度可能会在特朗普上台前失去影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-caution-on-ukraine-risks-loss-of-clout-ahead-of-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自俄罗斯全面入侵以来，英国就以大力支持乌克兰而闻名。但在首相基尔·斯塔默的任期内，泽连斯基总统的政府及其支持者对英国更为谨慎的做法越来越感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/starmer-s-caution-on-ukraine-risks-loss-of-clout-ahead-of-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 18:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
